家人的隐私，不希望儿子过多地曝光。尽管在娱乐圈中兄弟姐妹、父母和子女共同工作的情况并不鲜见，但像杨志刚这样的家庭，兄弟之间深厚的情感与相互扶持，实属难得。杨志刚通过自己...\n\n---\n\n标题：最新电视剧排行榜\nURL：http://tv.2345.com/top/new.html\n站点名称：2345电视剧\n发布时间：\n摘要：\n展开全部  \ue600 。女大学生夜爬遇害，同行好友各怀鬼胎，凶手偷天换日引发血案。器官贩卖团伙头目被人摘肾，缺失的肾竟然出现在了受害人体内。断指...  展开全部  \ue600', 'id': 'lc_78783260-286b-49b3-9225-f968c4844006'}], name='common_search', id='254519aa-aff6-4a8a-8759-f9b8126631bc', tool_call_id='call_00f6e694aeed4f5681bfb2c5'), AIMessage(content='', additional_kwargs={'refusal': None}, response_metadata={'token_usage': {'completion_tokens': 42, 'prompt_tokens': 6566, 'total_tokens': 6608, 'completion_tokens_details': {'accepted_prediction_tokens': None, 'audio_tokens': None, 'reasoning_tokens': 0, 'rejected_prediction_tokens': None, 'text_tokens': 42}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'audio_tokens': None, 'cached_tokens': None, 'text_tokens': 6566}}, 'model_provider': 'openai', 'model_name': 'qwen3.5-plus', 'system_fingerprint': None, 'id': 'chatcmpl-a447f8ae-a882-908c-a6ea-29b6b5d46c8b', 'finish_reason': 'tool_calls', 'logprobs': None}, name='researcher', id='lc_run--019c9f29-1a09-7ea1-9686-06a024df1c2c-0', tool_calls=[{'name': 'common_search', 'args': {'query': '编剧 哥哥是导演 妻子是导演 欧洲 短篇小说改编'}, 'id': 'call_467e2406c9ae47c187e9d58f', 'type': 'tool_call'}], invalid_tool_calls=[], usage_metadata={'input_tokens': 6566, 'output_tokens': 42, 'total_tokens': 6608, 'input_token_details': {}, 'output_token_details': {'reasoning': 0}}), ToolMessage(content="SYSTEM ALERT: You have used the tool 'common_search' 3 times, which is the limit for a single tool. You MUST switch to a DIFFERENT search tool (e.g., use 'academic_search' or 'web_search' instead of 'common_search'). Using the same tool repeatedly is ineffective. TRY ANOTHER TOOL.", name='common_search', id='9c9d392f-7554-479d-990c-b63cfaece898', tool_call_id='call_467e2406c9ae47c187e9d58f'), AIMessage(content='', additional_kwargs={'refusal': None}, response_metadata={'token_usage': {'completion_tokens': 213, 'prompt_tokens': 6690, 'total_tokens': 6903, 'completion_tokens_details': {'accepted_prediction_tokens': None, 'audio_tokens': None, 'reasoning_tokens': 171, 'rejected_prediction_tokens': None, 'text_tokens': 213}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'audio_tokens': None, 'cached_tokens': None, 'text_tokens': 6690}}, 'model_provider': 'openai', 'model_name': 'qwen3.5-plus', 'system_fingerprint': None, 'id': 'chatcmpl-f2142450-c987-98c0-b3aa-cf56805581dc', 'finish_reason': 'tool_calls', 'logprobs': None}, name='researcher', id='lc_run--019c9f29-1ef1-7041-b325-35d72a677cf8-0', tool_calls=[{'name': 'wikipedia', 'args': {'__arg1': '欧洲编剧 哥哥导演 妻子导演 短篇小说改编电影'}, 'id': 'call_43cf48bc91074c7293547554', 'type': 'tool_call'}], invalid_tool_calls=[], usage_metadata={'input_tokens': 6690, 'output_tokens': 213, 'total_tokens': 6903, 'input_token_details': {}, 'output_token_details': {'reasoning': 171}}), ToolMessage(content='No good Wikipedia Search Result was found', name='wikipedia', id='c337a316-b5d9-4cc8-980a-32b7a94f3296', tool_call_id='call_43cf48bc91074c7293547554'), AIMessage(content='', additional_kwargs={'refusal': None}, response_metadata={'token_usage': {'completion_tokens': 42, 'prompt_tokens': 6752, 'total_tokens': 6794, 'completion_tokens_details': {'accepted_prediction_tokens': None, 'audio_tokens': None, 'reasoning_tokens': 0, 'rejected_prediction_tokens': None, 'text_tokens': 42}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'audio_tokens': None, 'cached_tokens': None, 'text_tokens': 6752}}, 'model_provider': 'openai', 'model_name': 'qwen3.5-plus', 'system_fingerprint': None, 'id': 'chatcmpl-61e8687f-b4ea-9019-86d6-c7534059e7c0', 'finish_reason': 'tool_calls', 'logprobs': None}, name='researcher', id='lc_run--019c9f29-39cc-7be2-9a84-98865add1240-0', tool_calls=[{'name': 'common_search', 'args': {'query': '"哥哥是导演" "妻子是导演" 编剧 欧洲'}, 'id': 'call_428fe214185c438a9ad3eb9d', 'type': 'tool_call'}], invalid_tool_calls=[], usage_metadata={'input_tokens': 6752, 'output_tokens': 42, 'total_tokens': 6794, 'input_token_details': {}, 'output_token_details': {'reasoning': 0}}), ToolMessage(content="SYSTEM ALERT: You have used the tool 'common_search' 3 times, which is the limit for a single tool. You MUST switch to a DIFFERENT search tool (e.g., use 'academic_search' or 'web_search' instead of 'common_search'). Using the same tool repeatedly is ineffective. TRY ANOTHER TOOL.", name='common_search', id='5a2ef9c4-96b6-4272-ad1c-f99f8464d326', tool_call_id='call_428fe214185c438a9ad3eb9d'), AIMessage(content='', additional_kwargs={'refusal': None}, response_metadata={'token_usage': {'completion_tokens': 43, 'prompt_tokens': 6876, 'total_tokens': 6919, 'completion_tokens_details': {'accepted_prediction_tokens': None, 'audio_tokens': None, 'reasoning_tokens': 0, 'rejected_prediction_tokens': None, 'text_tokens': 43}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'audio_tokens': None, 'cached_tokens': None, 'text_tokens': 6876}}, 'model_provider': 'openai', 'model_name': 'qwen3.5-plus', 'system_fingerprint': None, 'id': 'chatcmpl-fbc89b0f-0db6-96f6-921f-09e96c76ce70', 'finish_reason': 'tool_calls', 'logprobs': None}, name='researcher', id='lc_run--019c9f29-3f2a-7183-a178-3982b3d8e7d5-0', tool_calls=[{'name': 'academic_search', 'args': {'__arg1': 'screenwriter brother director wife director Europe short story film two narrative lines'}, 'id': 'call_2b3ad9d5c4de4afd878904ea', 'type': 'tool_call'}], invalid_tool_calls=[], usage_metadata={'input_tokens': 6876, 'output_tokens': 43, 'total_tokens': 6919, 'input_token_details': {}, 'output_token_details': {'reasoning': 0}}), ToolMessage(content="Published: 2021-04-28\nTitle: Moving frames and compatibility conditions for three-dimensional director fields\nAuthors: Luiz C. B. da Silva, Efi Efrati\nSummary: The geometry and topology of the region in which a director field is embedded impose limitations on the kind of supported orientational order. These limitations manifest as compatibility conditions that relate the quantities describing the director field to the geometry of the embedding space. For example, in two dimensions (2D) the splay and bend fields suffice to determine a director uniquely (up to rigid motions) and must comply with one relation linear in the Gaussian curvature of the embedding manifold. In 3D there are additional local fields describing the director, i.e. fields available to a local observer residing within the material, and a number of distinct ways to yield geometric frustration. So far it was unknown how many such local fields are required to uniquely describe a 3D director field, nor what are the compatibility relations they must satisfy. In this work, we address these questions directly. We employ the method of moving frames to show that a director field is fully determined by five local fields. These fields are shown to be related to each other and to the curvature of the embedding space through six differential relations. As an application of our method, we characterize all uniform distortion director fields, i.e., directors for which all the local characterizing fields are constant in space, in manifolds of constant curvature. The classification of such phases has been recently provided for directors in Euclidean space, where the textures correspond to foliations of space by parallel congruent helices. For non-vanishing curvature, we show that the pure twist phase is the only solution in positively curved space, while in the hyperbolic space uniform distortion fields correspond to foliations of space by (non-necessarily parallel) congruent helices. Further analysis is expected to allow to also construct of new non-uniform director fields.\n\nPublished: 2024-08-19\nTitle: Anim-Director: A Large Multimodal Model Powered Agent for Controllable Animation Video Generation\nAuthors: Yunxin Li, Haoyuan Shi, Baotian Hu, Longyue Wang, Jiashun Zhu, Jinyi Xu, Zhen Zhao, Min Zhang\nSummary: Traditional animation generation methods depend on training generative models with human-labelled data, entailing a sophisticated multi-stage pipeline that demands substantial human effort and incurs high training costs. Due to limited prompting plans, these methods typically produce brief, information-poor, and context-incoherent animations. To overcome these limitations and automate the animation process, we pioneer the introduction of large multimodal models (LMMs) as the core processor to build an autonomous animation-making agent, named Anim-Director. This agent mainly harnesses the advanced understanding and reasoning capabilities of LMMs and generative AI tools to create animated videos from concise narratives or simple instructions. Specifically, it operates in three main stages: Firstly, the Anim-Director generates a coherent storyline from user inputs, followed by a detailed director's script that encompasses settings of character profiles and interior/exterior descriptions, and context-coherent scene descriptions that include appearing characters, interiors or exteriors, and scene events. Secondly, we employ LMMs with the image generation tool to produce visual images of settings and scenes. These images are designed to maintain visual consistency across different scenes using a visual-language prompting method that combines scene descriptions and images of the appearing character and setting. Thirdly, scene images serve as the foundation for producing animated videos, with LMMs generating prompts to guide this process. The whole process is notably autonomous without manual intervention, as the LMMs interact seamlessly with generative tools to generate prompts", name='academic_search', id='a2a90bee-4125-481b-8bfd-e5e586d2a908', tool_call_id='call_2b3ad9d5c4de4afd878904ea'), AIMessage(content='', additional_kwargs={'refusal': None}, response_metadata={'token_usage': {'completion_tokens': 38, 'prompt_tokens': 7698, 'total_tokens': 7736, 'completion_tokens_details': {'accepted_prediction_tokens': None, 'audio_tokens': None, 'reasoning_tokens': 0, 'rejected_prediction_tokens': None,